  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large tagliere vessel over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until translucent, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for an additional 1 minute.",
    "Add the buckwheat and cook, stirring constantly, for 2 minutes.",
    "Add the grilled chicken, diced tomato, crumbled feta cheese, dried oregano, salt, and pepper, and stir to combine.",
    "Reduce heat to low and simmer, covered, for 10 minutes.",
    "Fluff the pilaf with a fork and serve hot.",
    "Garnish with additional feta cheese and a sprinkle of oregano, if desired."
